Marjorie Kane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Kane 0 Marjorie Kane (April 28, 1909 – January 8, 1992) was an American film and stage actress born in Chicago. She appeared in 68 films between 1929 and 1951, occasionally under the name Babe Kane. Marjorie_Kane ( April_28_,_1909 – January_8_,_1992 ) was an_American_film_and_stage_actress born in Chicago .
